  "intro": "<p>  </p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, \" e;helvetica=\"\" neue\"e;,=\"\" e;pingfang=\"\" sc\"e;,=\"\" e;hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\"e;,=\"\" e;microsoft=\"\" yahei\"e;,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 25.6px;=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" !important;=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" span=\"\" 《菩提之下》是桑吉平措与歌友成功合作《礼赞》之后，再度与歌友（词作家“王小雅”老师）合作完成的一首优秀作品。=\"\" p=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">         </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, \" e;helvetica=\"\" neue\"e;,=\"\" e;pingfang=\"\" sc\"e;,=\"\" e;hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\"e;,=\"\" e;microsoft=\"\" yahei\"e;,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 25.6px;=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" !important;=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" span=\"\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">这首作品的出炉，也是桑吉平措多次受邀参加华人“中日和平友好文化交流”后，在参观了中国唐代大德鉴真和尚的庙宇，并亲自瞻仰了鉴真和尚当年带去的菩提树，而特别纪念鉴真法师为和平友好所做出的卓越贡献而献礼。这首歌曲风婉转又感情深挚，既平静欢喜，又表达出内心的崇敬。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, \" e;helvetica=\"\" neue\"e;,=\"\" e;pingfang=\"\" sc\"e;,=\"\" e;hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\"e;,=\"\" e;microsoft=\"\" yahei\"e;,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 25.6px;=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" !important;=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" p=\"\">         </p>",
